ID REGLA: $flaglogic$
Retardo i: $retardoTipoDoc_A$
Retardo j: $retardoTipoDoc_B$

INSERT INTO compensadosPatrimoniales
SELECT saknr, kunnr, lifnr, blart, bldat, budat, azbet, dmbtr, sgtxt, belnr, azwae, hwaer, buzei, gjahr, shkzg, record_id, signo, compensado
FROM (
    SELECT
        A.*,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY A.kunnr ORDER BY A.dmbtr, A.blart) AS row_num
    FROM
        pa_patrimoniales A
    JOIN pa_patrimoniales B ON
        ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$') OR (A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
    WHERE
        A.kunnr = B.kunnr
    	and A.record_id <> B.record_id
        AND A.signo <> B.signo
        AND A.dmbtr - B.dmbtr = 0
        AND A.compensado = false
        AND B.compensado = false
) AS CompensacionesA
WHERE row_num = 1
UNION
SELECT saknr, kunnr, lifnr, blart, bldat, budat, azbet, dmbtr, sgtxt, belnr, azwae, hwaer, buzei, gjahr, shkzg, record_id, signo, compensado
FROM (
    SELECT
        B.*,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY A.kunnr ORDER BY A.dmbtr, A.blart) AS row_num
    FROM
        pa_patrimoniales B
    JOIN pa_patrimoniales A ON
       ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$') OR (A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
    WHERE
        A.kunnr = B.kunnr
    	and A.record_id <> B.record_id
        AND A.signo <> B.signo
        AND A.dmbtr - B.dmbtr = 0
        AND A.compensado = false
        AND B.compensado = false
) AS CompensacionesB
WHERE row_num = 1

INSERT INTO compensadosPatrimoniales
select
	A.*
from
	pa_patrimoniales A
join pa_patrimoniales B 
on
	A.bldat = B.bldat
	and (A.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A$%' OR A.sgtxt LIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A$%')
	and (B.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B$%' OR B.sgtxt LIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B$%')
	and ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' and B.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$') or (A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' and B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
where
	A.record_id <> B.record_id
	AND A.signo <> B.signo
	AND ABS(A.azbet - B.azbet) <= $limRedondeo$ 
	and A.compensado = false 
	and B.compensado = false
UNION
select
	B.*
from
	pa_patrimoniales B
join pa_patrimoniales A 
on
	A.bldat = B.bldat
	and (A.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A$%' OR A.sgtxt LIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A$%')
	and (B.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B$%' OR B.sgtxt LIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B$%')
	and ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' and B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
where
	A.record_id <> B.record_id
	AND A.signo <> B.signo
	AND ABS(A.azbet - B.azbet) <= $limRedondeo$ 
	and A.compensado = false 
	and B.compensado = false
order by azbet,blart
